{"word":"G1106 - γνώμη - gnṓmē - gno'-may - Advice","slug":"G1106","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">γνώμη</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gnṓmē"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gno'-may"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Advice"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B3;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03B7; - gno&#x0304;me&#x0304;</b> - <i>gno'-may</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1097\">G1097</a>; <i>cognition</i>, that is, (subjectively) <i>opinion</i>, or (objectively) <i>resolve</i> (<i>counsel</i>, <i>consent</i>, etc.): - advice, + agree, judgment, mind, purpose, will."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1097\">G1097</a>, <a href=\"#/G1107\">G1107</a>, <a href=\"#/G1108\">G1108</a>, <a href=\"#/G1110\">G1110</a>, <a href=\"#/G176\">G176</a>, <a href=\"#/G1921\">G1921</a>, <a href=\"#/G1922\">G1922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2607\">G2607</a>, <a href=\"#/G4267\">G4267</a>, <a href=\"#/G4268\">G4268</a>, <a href=\"#/G4774\">G4774</a>"}]}